product_name: Anastasia Beverly HillsDual-Ended Cream to Powder Perfect Brow Pencil
summary: SummaryHighlightsCruelty FreeVeganPerfect Brow Pencil by Anastasia Beverly Hills is a traditional wooden pencil with a powder-like formula for filling and defining brows. This easy-to-use brow pencil also features a custom spoolie end for blending the product to a natural-looking matte finish.
